{"tid":675953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂呀, 玩撚夠未呀 - 【貿易戰】特朗普促查汽車及零件進口","createTime":"2018-05-24T03:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T06:19:28.000Z","uid":7369,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8b4b399f5b927185e24c0c8723a2810cdac224","tid":675953,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:46:08.000Z","msg":"中國商務部：濫用國內法 <br />\n<br />\n 白宮發表聲明稱，美國總統特朗普指示商務部長羅斯「考慮對包括卡車在內的汽車、汽車零組件進口展開232條款調查，以決定這類進口對美國國家安全的影響。」<br />\n<br />\n中國商務部發言人則表示，中方反對美國濫用國內法，將密切關注美方汽車232調查進展，對可能的影響進行全面評估。中國早前宣佈，自7月1日起將乘用車進口關稅稅率從25%降至15%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，特朗普於Twitter中表示，與中國的貿易談判進展理想，但最終會於不同結構，因此要完成及檢閱結果仍然困難。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180524/58230604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58230604&d=24PkLJ6Ty%2FO0VFS1NGPvhywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9672024e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58230604&h=f3aafb17\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180524/58230604</a>"},{"pid":"15a744b923a6fcc857f2ae2de00a560d5f73cf4e","tid":675953,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e345c0e949a92f25d57461ba916928826e815dfd","tid":675953,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:53:18.000Z","msg":"又贏，贏完再贏，贏到開巷"},{"pid":"6ad1f5c8210bcff69d3c4198df7bc94161f35bde","tid":675953,"uid":50386,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"人地地响自己國家用自己法律都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />